{"tid":1868143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"根本香港人就抵死 輸撚梗","createTime":"2020-02-07T11:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T12:39:45.000Z","uid":60916,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5e3dcf7126b1bfa7ba24b2cbe3f000b33b66ad39","tid":1868143,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:59:14.000Z","msg":"醫護罷工一星期<br />\n期間完全無其他工會一齊加入罷工行例<br />\n<br />\n就算有,當中又有幾多人肯罷工?<br />\n<br />\n問題出左係邊?<br />\n就係好多香港人買左樓,供緊樓<br />\n罷工既人擔心被炒,無糧出點算,點供樓?<br />\n所以點解政府唔可以比樓價跌,點解政府唔會起多D樓,點解政府會比樓支那人先過香港人<br />\n<br />\n因為佢就係要你地爭,要你地成世做樓奴,咁就無可能反抗<br />\n供完既-&gt;唔想層樓跌價,,唔會理D乜訴求,話撚知你<br />\n未供完既-&gt;無本錢罷工<br />\n所以點解最後最活躍既通常都係學生,都係一D基層,大多數都係唔洗供樓<br />\n即係政府只要拖下,最後跪既一定唔係港共<br />\n就算港共有幾仆街,反抗既人數都係有限<br />\n<br />\n可能好多人覺得我係度放負<br />\n但事實就係咁,出左黎做野既,問心啦,要搞罷工你供緊樓你肯唔肯?<br />\n唔介意你地屌我<br />\n但我相信屌我既9成9都係供緊樓,然後講句,你有冇罷工,你知唔知我有負擔<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係點解香港人到依家爭取乜都失敗既原因<br />\n屌我既人 如果你地覺得出下POST就當撐左,捐下錢就當撐左,然後衰左就話<br />\n今次進步左架啦,下次會更好,唔好放負呀,放負既係3毛,想搞散民心<br />\n想問下你地,就算真係有下次,下次你又願意做D乜?咪又係講句加油,捐下錢當做左野<br />\n屌,如果咁既心態,就唔好搞抗爭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n肯罷工,肯抗爭既人,係犧牲左好多野去抗爭<br />\n並唔係講句支持,唔係捐左錢就參加左<br />\n如果真係無呢個抗爭既心態,真係唔好搞抗爭<br />\n因為會令到好多真係抗爭既手足,有無限既後果,但結果因為參加既人唔多<br />\n而呢班抗爭既手足就變左condom<br />\n<br />\n醒下啦,香港人,ok?<br />\n<br />\n歡迎樓下既人開始屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我認清自己有試過罷工,見盡身邊黃色朋友,同事無參與過罷工呢個事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人都知抗爭有後果,但只要承擔後果既唔係自己就OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n100個有99個都係呢種心態,點抗爭成功?<br />\n<br />\n我相信好多人睇完唔敢推<br />\n因為自己就係呢種人,怕比人識穿"},{"pid":"bc2b467c6f203d4be4c2c2960d209997a5854ee9","tid":1868143,"uid":198590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:59:33.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#60916 - 山齊士超級綠洲</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請保持批判性思考，善用「上一頁」和「不推文回覆」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">該會員以往言論 (7)：</div><code>1 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eQijrT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eQijrT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>2 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eBHfvT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eBHfvT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠, 做假新聞</span><br />\n<code>3 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eAEteT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eAEteT</a><span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n<code>4 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/esqExT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/esqExT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>5 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/esqBmT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/esqBmT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">洗白黑警</span><br />\n<code>6 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/epmkQT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/epmkQT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍言論</span><br />\n<code>7 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/epmfaT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/epmfaT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍言論</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">「歷史回顧，無忘初心」</div><pre><code data-type=\"\">2019年9月29日\n抗中共反納粹全球集會</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GwyoBij.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGwyoBij.jpg&h=e72616bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7JPONpW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7JPONpW.jpg&h=4a8f141d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">「文宣」</div><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KYk2LaK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKYk2LaK.jpg&h=478fd3f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a>"},{"pid":"8e76271aa78e79a95175f5793ba563a458139469","tid":1868143,"uid":331861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:04:11.000Z","msg":"跟住下次政府就會話<br />\n全港所有人要繼續返工但係出街唔可以帶口罩<br />\n如果唔係就聯同你公司高層炒你魷魚<br />\n咁呢個政策就會百分百即刻推行到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80a6e85542339403eb2e8f357fdbf622241796a","tid":1868143,"uid":266100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:04:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa1a0a471159c6aa46125369e23e9d825207a31b","tid":1868143,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:30:05.000Z","msg":"輸乜春呀輸？"},{"pid":"01dc9a0e9c52a6e5a0311b2bbb23367934caf828","tid":1868143,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:37:07.000Z","msg":"用把口支持係無用，要用實際行動<br />\n<br />\n既然香港暫時勇武同罷工都係唔可行，咁唯有 焦土<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1868045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1868045</a><br />\n<br />\n[香港人，反抗] 要贏，必須升級至 全民三罷，甚至 全民勇武<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1866282\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1866282</a><br />\n<br />\n無論係 <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勇武</span></strong></span> 或者 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">罷緊工</span></span></strong> 既手足 都捱唔到好耐<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「我地以為一二一二係衝，點知人地一二一二係退既。」<br />\n<br />\n「望返後面已經冇晒人。」<br />\n<br />\n「如果佢話三罷，或者罷鐵、罷藍舖頭，講完你要真係做先得架。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n擺在面前有兩套方法，<br />\n其一是  <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">全民有心理準備作正面衝突</span>，<br />\n其二是  <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">全民落實罷工</span><br />\n<br />\n「但係好多人就係覺得，去到呢個樽頸唔知點做。其實佢心入面明明就知呢兩樣野。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「希望大家唔好淨係識得講香港人反抗，反抗係做出?架，唔係你鳩?架！」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「我地個個都有夢想架，我地個個都有?野想做，但係，我地肯犧牲??野?上前線爭取啊！」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n勇武 同 醫護 都唔係condom，<br />\n所有珍惜生命既香港人，<br />\n以及願意付出更多既抗爭者，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">請你地加入呢次罷工！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n對於全民勇武已經唔抱太大既希望，但係呢次武漢肺炎係一個發動罷工既大好機會<br />\n希望全香港人可以真正團結一次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vzoa9L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vzoa9L.png&h=f8666165&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3054930cd7d8ab722e99fb69a890c4dc39b4ce0f","tid":1868143,"uid":73598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:39:45.000Z","msg":"有冇方法又供到樓又罷到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}